%div#content
  %div.col.one
    %section.section
      %h1 Meetups
      %p Our meetups are open to all experience levels, from total novices to expert Rubyists. Do come along!

      .vevent
        %h2.summary TDD &amp; Getting Started with Jekyll

        %h3.when-icon.icon When?
        %p
          %span.dtstart
            - date_string = '2014-03-04'
            - date = Date.parse date_string
            %abbr.value{ :title => "#{date_string}" } #{date.strftime("#{date.day.ordinalize} %B, %Y")}
            %span.value 6:30pm

        %h3.where-icon.icon
          Where?
          %a.get-directions{ :href => "https://maps.google.com/maps?f=d&source=s_d&saddr=&hl=en&ie=UTF8&layer=c&daddr=54.5925564,-5.927705", :title => "ShopKeep POS"} Get Directions

        %p.location
          ShopKeep POS
          %br
          Alexander House, 1st Floor (Above Limelight), 17 Ormeau Avenue, Belfast, BT2 8HD

        %h3.what-icon.icon What?
        %p.description
          This month we're holding two talks catered to both the experienced Ruby developers and the newcomers, as well as workshops to help you get started.

        %h4 Test Driven Development
        %p.description
          %a{:href => 'https://twitter.com/brrygrdn'}Barry Gordon
          from
          %a{:href => 'http://www.shopkeep.com/'}ShopKeep
          will be talking about TDD, disucssing how you can use the principles in your Ruby development process. He'll be lending a helping hand during the workshops with getting set up with TDD/Ruby learning tool, Ruby Koans.

        %h4 Jekyll and Github Pages
        %p.description
          Following this,
          %a{:href => 'https://twitter.com/cobyism'}Coby Chapple
          from
          %a{:href => 'http://www.github.com/'}GitHub
          will be demonstrating how to set up a free website using Jekyll, a ruby-based open source static site generator, and deploy it using GitHub Pages.

          Bring your laptop if you'd like help on getting your Jekyll sites up and running on the night.

        %a.url.cta{:href=> "http://digitalcircle.org/events/belfast-ruby-tdd-getting-started-with-jekyll"} Attend Meetup >
